%% EvalHub Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.1/eval-hub.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard / API)
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Application<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking Server<br/>5000/TCP or 443/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AdapterJob as Adapter Job Pod<br/>(lm-eval / GuideLLM / LightEval)
    participant Storage as Storage<br/>(SQLite / PostgreSQL)

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Create and Execute Evaluation Job

    Client->>KRBP: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token (SA)
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(RBAC validation)
    KRBP->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>HTTP/8080, localhost (pre-authenticated)
    EvalHub->>EvalHub: Validate request payload<br/>(go-playground/validator)
    EvalHub->>MLflow: Create/Get Experiment<br/>HTTP(S), SA projected token, TLS 1.2+
    MLflow-->>EvalHub: Experiment ID
    EvalHub->>Storage: Store evaluation job record
    Storage-->>EvalHub: Job ID
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (benchmark config)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: ConfigMap created
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create batch/v1 Job (per benchmark)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Job created
    EvalHub-->>KRBP: 201 Created (Job ID)
    KRBP-->>Client: 201 Created (Job ID)

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: Adapter Job Reports Results Back

    K8sAPI->>AdapterJob: Pod scheduled and started
    AdapterJob->>AdapterJob: Execute evaluation benchmark
    AdapterJob->>MLflow: Log metrics and artifacts<br/>HTTP(S), projected SA token (1h TTL)
    MLflow-->>AdapterJob: OK
    AdapterJob->>KRBP: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token (projected SA)
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview
    KRBP->>EvalHub: POST events<br/>HTTP/8080 (pre-authenticated)
    EvalHub->>Storage: Update benchmark status
    Storage-->>EvalHub: Updated
    EvalHub-->>KRBP: 200 OK
    KRBP-->>AdapterJob: 200 OK

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: Query Evaluation Status

    Client->>KRBP: GET /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    KRBP->>EvalHub: GET /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}<br/>HTTP/8080
    EvalHub->>Storage: Query job record
    Storage-->>EvalHub: Job details + benchmark statuses
    EvalHub-->>KRBP: 200 OK (JSON response)
    KRBP-->>Client: 200 OK (JSON response)
